{"tid":2284094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣自主研發騰雲大型無人機進行測試 將來有望可用作發射反艦飛彈","createTime":"2020-11-13T04:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T05:39:15.000Z","uid":292499,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3c5089e473f86397f3cbdbe116b159b32a41cd","tid":2284094,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"......<br />\n<br />\n熟知內情的軍方人士今天說，「騰雲」無人機是中科院自研自製的大型無人機，定位在多功能丶多用途的空中無人載台，由於是自研自製，自然不會掛載由其他國家採購而來的武器系統，他研判認為，若第一階段是進行2.75吋空射火箭與劍一飛彈的掛載驗證，下一階段即有可能進行空射型雄二飛彈的測試，讓二代「騰雲」無人機具有對海對地攻擊戰力。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3350568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3350568&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=88ca0685\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3350568&h=29e2f8e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3350568</a>"},{"pid":"946f9bebac0d30d4793121254ca4a361167a317f","tid":2284094,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:52:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2bcafbbdfeab29288888abfddf561368ed96f14","tid":2284094,"uid":292499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"其實外觀睇落同MQ-9一樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99eccc6befd4f4fb45e732807beffcb219cbf37f","tid":2284094,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":